    "In December 2023, the user @danshipper shared an unexpected problem regarding text and image processing software on the social media platform X foot_0.",
    "To his astonishment, a command that had worked flawlessly a short time before no longer worked.",
    "He uploaded an image of a book page, hoping to get the text back digitized, and in his helplessness posted his question to the public community.",
    "In response to his why, @NickADobos suggested: \"Hallucination.",
    "In part because you phrased it as a polite question, which 'no' is a valid answer to.\""
